snippet.title: Quest Master - Official Announcement Trailer | Guerrilla Collective 2023 Showcase
snippet.description: Check out the announcement trailer for Quest Master, an upcoming dungeon maker inspired by the classics. In Quest Master, unleash your imagination, alone or in local co-op, to make dungeons full of puzzles, traps, and monsters. Upload them for others to explore and challenge yourself with other players’ creations. Quest Master will be available in Early Access in July 2023. A demo is available now on Steam.
